text: Cheyenne van den Goorbergh (born 6 September 1997) is a Dutch football midfielder who plays for PEC Zwolle in the Eredivisie. ==International career== On 3 March 2018, she made her debut for the Netherlands women's national football team against Denmark and scored first goal for the Netherlands. ===International goals=== :Scores and results list the Netherlands goal tally first. {| class="wikitable" !
